author: Claudene Strickland
text: I'm sick of people comparing their tired to mine. Just say you're tired, that's it.

author: Claudene Strickland
text: Having "enough sleep" doesn't make a person tired, its how you spend your energy that makes a person tired.

author: Claudene Strickland
text:
I observed someone go from themself to someone else. I saw depletion. I felt their anger more than their light. I wept for their loss. I celebrate for their win.
-CKS

text:

author: Claudene Strickland
text:
I don't fall in love with people, I fall in love with habits and how that allows you to operate. So healthy habits is preferred.
Thank you.

author: Claudene Strickland
text:
Some people may not have changed, but I have.

Your car is faster than MINE
Your music is louder than MINE
Your house is more expensive than MINE.

In the end I focus on MINE 😉

text:

Thank you...

author: Claudene Strickland
text:
How do I stop myself from inadequate thinking?

I take a deep breath or 5 and think about the things I'm grateful for. I then tell myself out loud. "You have nothing better to do right now than close your eyes and sleep".

Works every time.
